<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>إِنَّ اللّاهَ لاا يَأْمُرُ بِالْفَحْشااءِ <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
